        <tr><td>Konnected Joe igniter (out-of-warranty)</td><td>$340 to $580</td></tr>
        <tr><td>iKamand WiFi controller module</td><td>$260 to $440</td></tr>
        <tr><td>iKamand fan motor or temperature probe</td><td>$200 to $380</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Konnected Joe automatic damper actuator</td><td>$260 to $440</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Hardware (draft door, hinge, dampers)</td><td>$80 to $280</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Out-of-warranty ceramic (Classic)</td><td>$340 to $580</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Out-of-warranty ceramic (Big Joe)</td><td>$440 to $780</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Warranty (SDAR labor)</td><td>90 days parts and labor on our work</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-number">Why us for Kamado Joe</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">What separates our Kamado Joe service.</h2>
    <ul class="reasons-list">
      <li><strong>Konnected Joe early-production igniter expertise.</strong> The 2023+ electric auto-ignition system has a recognizable early-failure pattern; we've seen it enough to call it on the phone before dispatching.</li>
      <li><strong>iKamand smart hub diagnostic.</strong> WiFi connectivity, fan motor, temperature probe, controller module. We run the right tree on each call.</li>
      <li><strong>Two service trees on one brand.</strong> Traditional ceramic on Classic and Big Joe; hybrid electric on Konnected Joe. We don't conflate them.</li>
      <li><strong>Masterbuilt warranty coordination.</strong> We file Konnected Joe igniter warranty claims and ceramic warranty claims on the customer's behalf when applicable.</li>
      <li><strong>Parts on the van.</strong> Classic and Big Joe gaskets, replacement dome thermometers, common fastener hardware.</li>
      <li><strong>BHGS #A49573 plus EPA 608 Universal certified #1346255700410.</strong> Verifiable.</li>
      <li><strong>Same-day across LA, OC, Ventura.</strong> Next-day for Riverside and San Bernardino. 24/7 phone.</li>
      <li><strong>BBB Accredited verifiable.</strong> See our <a href="/credentials/licensed/">license credentials</a>.</li>
    </ul>
